d. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outwit adversaries by masking your intentions, feigning attacks with nimble dashes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And when victory is within sight, unleash devastating strikes to claim your honor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/acc0b211408742438b67beab6c96c486.poster.avif?t=1773323741\" width=590 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/acc0b211408742438b67beab6c96c486.webm?t=1773323741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/acc0b211408742438b67beab6c96c486.mp4?t=1773323741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
